casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Leon Lamonte CORNELIUS, Appellant. WD 80440 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: SEPTEMBER 11, 2018 Carol D. Jansen, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Dora Fichter, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Four: Mark D. Pfeiffer, Presiding Judge, Karen King Mitchell, Chief Judge, Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Leon L. Cornelius appeals from a judgment convicting him of possession of a controlled substance with intent to distribute under Section 195.211, RSMo Cum. Supp. 2003, a class B felony. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
